Package it.polimi.LM39.model.leaderpermanenteffect

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlreadyOccupiedTowerDiscount
    Permanent effect used by Filippo Brunelleschi the player with this effect wont pay the already occupied tower cost
    CardCoinDiscount
    Permanent effect used by Pico della Mirandola Permanent discount on card's cost
    CopyLeaderAbility
    Permanent effect used by Lorenzo de' Medici this effect allows the player to copy the effect of another player leader card the selected effect can't be changed
    DoubleResourcesFromDevelopment
    Permanent effect used by Santa Rita double the resources from development cards
    LeaderPermanentEffect
    class (can't be abstract because RuntimeAdapterFactory needs a concrete class) that will be extended by all leader permanent effects
    NoMilitaryRequirementsForTerritory
    Used by Cesare Borgia the player with this effect can get territories without respecting the military requirements
    PlaceFamilyMemberOnOccupiedSpace
    Used by Ludovico Ariosto it allows the player to place a member where the action space is already occupied
    SetColoredDicesValues
    Used by Lucrezia Borgia & Ludovico il Moro this effect changes the value of family members by setting them (Lucrezia Borgia) or increasing them (Ludovico il Moro)
    UncoloredMemberBonus
    Used by Sigismondo Malatesta this effect permanent increase the uncolored family member value
    VictoryForSupportingTheChurch
    Used by Sisto IV this effect gives the player victory points when he supports the church
